    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Oh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Oh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I keep on saying-- sticking to my story.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He doesn't want to believe me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then that [INAUDIBLE], that Volksdeutsche, came over there somehow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was like the town came around and one was talking to another.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He had a band, you know, like from the police, from the occupation army, was like watching or helping out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was a Volksdeutsche for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, yes, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, who knows you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow, it came out that he knows me from before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he tells the story that I asked him about if I'm a passerby, if I have to.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he told me that I have to give that and I didn't.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He wanted to-- anyway, to make the story-- it took quite a while, back and forth, back and forth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're going to stop here and we'll continue.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
